snippet.title: Dark Amber Wakes Up Early And Gets Caught And Grounded
snippet.description:
Plot:
Dark Amber is about to go watch YouTube on the computer, Amber came in to her room and told her it was time for house chores. Dark Amber tried to refuse, but Amber made her get to work on chores around the house. After 2 hours, Dark Amber got fed up with her good imposter wasted her fun time by doing house chores. Dark Amber came up with an idea, she started planning on waking up at 5am were she doesn’t have to be forced to do chores. At 5 in the morning, Dark Amber woke up tired and groggy, she got up and went to go on the computer and watch YouTube. Meanwhile with Amber, she got up and went to bathroom. When Dark Amber got her computer turned on, she went to click the video what she want to watch on YouTube. But her computer was too loud, Dark Amber forgot to turn down the volume and went to quickly turn it down. When Amber finished her bathroom break and she was about to go to back to her bed, she heard that noise coming from Dark Amber’s bedroom. Amber found out she is not in bed and she went to Dark Amber’s bedroom, caught her playing on the computer watching YouTube while she is not in bed and got angry at her, Dark Amber got grounded by her good imposter and got sent back to bed.

Hope you enjoy the show?! 🎬🎥
